[[Category:en/Patch Settings]]
== Description ==
In case you have several vehicles (trains, trucks etc.) waiting for one type of cargo on a station it is much more effective to force loading a first arrived unit and only after it is full and ready to go start loading next (First-In-First-Out = FIFO).

== Use ==
This patch is disabled by default. You can enable this patch through the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Construction|configure patches -> stations]] window or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:

<pre>
[patches]
improved_load = true
</pre>